| [Disposing](system.windows.forms.control.disposing#system-windows-forms-control-disposing) | 获取一个值，该值指示基 [Control](system.windows.forms.control) 类是否正在处理。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Dock](system.windows.forms.control.dock#system-windows-forms-control-dock) | 获取或设置哪些控件边框停靠到其父控件，并确定控件如何调整其父级的大小。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [DockPadding](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol.dockpadding#system-windows-forms-scrollablecontrol-dockpadding) | 获取控件的所有边缘的停靠填充设置。<br> (继承自 [ScrollableControl](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol)) |  |
| [DoubleBuffered](system.windows.forms.control.doublebuffered#system-windows-forms-control-doublebuffered) | 获取或设置一个值，该值指示此控件是否应使用辅助缓冲区重新绘制其表面以减少或防止闪烁。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Enabled](system.windows.forms.control.enabled#system-windows-forms-control-enabled) | 获取或设置一个值，该值指示控件是否可以响应用户交互。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Events](system.componentmodel.component.events#system-componentmodel-component-events) | 获取附加到此 [Component](system.componentmodel.component)对象的事件处理程序的列表。<br> (继承自 [Component](system.componentmodel.component)) |  |
| [Focused](system.windows.forms.control.focused#system-windows-forms-control-focused) | 获取一个值，该值指示控件是否具有输入焦点。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Font](system.windows.forms.control.font#system-windows-forms-control-font) | 获取或设置控件显示的文本的字体。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [FontHeight](system.windows.forms.control.fontheight#system-windows-forms-control-fontheight) | 获取或设置控件字体的高度。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [ForeColor](system.windows.forms.control.forecolor#system-windows-forms-control-forecolor) | 获取或设置控件的前景色。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Handle](system.windows.forms.control.handle#system-windows-forms-control-handle) | 获取控件绑定到的窗口句柄。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [HasChildren](system.windows.forms.control.haschildren#system-windows-forms-control-haschildren) | 获取一个值，该值指示控件是否包含一个或多个子控件。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Height](system.windows.forms.control.height#system-windows-forms-control-height) | 获取或设置控件的高度。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [HorizontalScroll](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol.horizontalscroll#system-windows-forms-scrollablecontrol-horizontalscroll) | 获取与水平滚动条关联的特征。<br> (继承自 [ScrollableControl](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol)) |  |
| [HScroll](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol.hscroll#system-windows-forms-scrollablecontrol-hscroll) | 获取或设置一个值，该值指示水平滚动条是否可见。<br> (继承自 [ScrollableControl](system.windows.forms.scrollablecontrol)) |  |
| [ImeMode](system.windows.forms.control.imemode#system-windows-forms-control-imemode) | 获取或设置控件的输入法编辑器 （IME） 模式。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [ImeModeBase](system.windows.forms.control.imemodebase#system-windows-forms-control-imemodebase) | 获取或设置控件的 IME 模式。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [InvokeRequired](system.windows.forms.control.invokerequired#system-windows-forms-control-invokerequired) | 获取一个值，该值指示调用方在对控件进行方法调用时是否必须调用调用方法，因为调用方与创建控件的线程不同。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [IsAccessible](system.windows.forms.control.isaccessible#system-windows-forms-control-isaccessible) | 获取或设置一个值，该值指示控件是否对辅助功能应用程序可见。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [IsAncestorSiteInDesignMode](system.windows.forms.control.isancestorsiteindesignmode#system-windows-forms-control-isancestorsiteindesignmode) | 指示此控件的上级位置之一是否位于 DesignMode 中。 此属性为只读。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [IsDisposed](system.windows.forms.control.isdisposed#system-windows-forms-control-isdisposed) | 获取一个值，该值指示控件是否已释放。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [IsHandleCreated](system.windows.forms.control.ishandlecreated#system-windows-forms-control-ishandlecreated) | 获取一个值，该值指示控件是否具有与之关联的句柄。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [IsMirrored](system.windows.forms.control.ismirrored#system-windows-forms-control-ismirrored) | 获取一个值，该值指示控件是否镜像。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [LayoutEngine](system.windows.forms.control.layoutengine#system-windows-forms-control-layoutengine) | 获取控件布局引擎的缓存实例。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Left](system.windows.forms.control.left#system-windows-forms-control-left) | 获取或设置控件左边缘与其容器工作区的左边缘之间的距离（以像素为单位）。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Location](system.windows.forms.control.location#system-windows-forms-control-location) | 获取或设置控件左上角相对于其容器左上角的坐标。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Margin](system.windows.forms.control.margin#system-windows-forms-control-margin) | 获取或设置控件之间的间距。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [MaximumSize](system.windows.forms.control.maximumsize#system-windows-forms-control-maximumsize) | 获取或设置可指定上限 [GetPreferredSize(Size)](system.windows.forms.control.getpreferredsize#system-windows-forms-control-getpreferredsize%28system-drawing-size%29) 的大小。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [MinimumSize](system.windows.forms.control.minimumsize#system-windows-forms-control-minimumsize) | 获取或设置可以指定的下限 [GetPreferredSize(Size)](system.windows.forms.control.getpreferredsize#system-windows-forms-control-getpreferredsize%28system-drawing-size%29) 的大小。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
| [Name](system.windows.forms.control.name#system-windows-forms-control-name) | 获取或设置控件的名称。<br> (继承自 [Control](system.windows.forms.control)) |  |
